  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，听好了，我们现在有个小麻烦。\n显然其他人也对那个货感兴趣。你为什么不向他们秀一下肌肉比比谁更有资格呢，嗯？你当然可以杀掉他们所有人，但我有个更好的主意。\n\n拿些更大的武器，比如机枪！对着周围扫射，干掉那些混蛋。也许这样他们就知道谁才是这里真正的大王了。毕竟我们的装备比他们更好。\n\n估计不久就会有客人到了。",
    "en": "Hey, listen up, we got a small problem now.\nApparently some other people got interested in that cargo aswell. How about you show them who deserves it more, hmm? You can kill all of them obviously, I got a better idea tho.\nTake something big, a machine gun or something, yes machine guns! Shoot around the area and kill some of these scumbags. Maybe then they know how the boss here is. After all we are better equipped than them anyway.\nExpect visitors."
  },
